a","tid":1842123,"uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T01:48:30.000Z","msg":"深圳封關喇求求你。遲左就大爆發了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9acfdfabfa29b1fe1199ca04cc5c141a1ecc3af","tid":1842123,"uid":74012,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T01:49:33.000Z","msg":"睇清楚<br />\n中英街同沙頭角口岸係兩樣嘢"},{"pid":"f29d5d21fc354039bd35cf043c21db793531907b","tid":1842123,"uid":328778,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"77aa86ba5fc54a8446985a0b5037c1432ef2757d","tid":1842123,"uid":259010,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T14:06:57.000Z","msg":"6天蓋出「火神山醫院」不夠用！武漢決定旁邊再蓋一所「雷神山」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4669/d4669737.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4669%2Fd4669737.jpg&h=1816b700&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>▲為了再6天內蓋出「火神山醫院」，大陸調動上百台挖土機整地。（圖／新華網）</strong><br />\n記者蔡紹堅／綜合報導<br />\n武漢市防疫指揮部23日決定參照SARS期間7天建成的「小湯山醫院」，在6天內興建一所武漢肺炎的專門醫院，定名為「火神山醫院」。不過，似乎是考量到「火神山」的床位有限，武漢市防疫指揮部25日下午決定，要在2月5日前在「火神山」旁再建一所「雷神山醫院」。<br />\n「火神山醫院」的承建單位中建三局人員透露，火神山醫院的面積為2.5萬平方公尺，可容納1000張床，規劃在6天內建成，也就是說會在2月1日完工，2月3日投入使用。<br />\n<strong>▼挖土機通宵趕工，為了達成6天蓋出醫院的目標。（圖／新華網）</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4669/d4669734.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4669%2Fd4669734.jpg&h=9699b0e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為了達成6天完工的目標，中建三局23日晚上就展開動作，調集上百台挖土機、推土機等施工機械抵達工地，通宵進行場平、回填等施工。主體的施工則從25日開始，整個施工期間，項目部將按照兩班倒的方式日夜不停施工，高峰期將有1500名建設者和280台套施工機械設備同時奮戰。<br />\n不過，似乎是考量到「火神山醫院」的1000個床位不夠用，武漢市防疫指揮部25日下午3點半舉行調度會，決定在「火神山醫院」旁邊，在2月5日前再建成一所「雷神山醫院」，新增床位1300張。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4669/d4669716.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4669%2Fd4669716.jpg&h=fa4a9f18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>▲武漢肺炎疫情嚴峻，多名醫護也遭感染。（圖／武漢中心醫院）</strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T01:51:21.000Z","msg":"其實係焚化爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432c02feb16c663a2b0b0dd84ee87aeba3b98fff","tid":1842123,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2339c8dbfd05df8f94dd09115401656a3464556","tid":1842123,"uid":2429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T14:08:37.000Z","msg":"支持深圳封城。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T02:31:43.000Z","msg":"依個嘅機會仲大"},{"pid":"c6b781e0ce3777d78c829357e858192f72274d17","tid":1842123,"uid":316700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fc99e676e34c882cc7fd26f7a32feada7df9ed2","tid":1842123,"uid":31962,"like":88,"dislike":1,"score":87,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T14:05:48.000Z","msg":"香港唔會封關<br />\n但大陸會先封晒香港啲關<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T02:32:20.000Z","msg":"咁係咪好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a787c79e95aabf4799c3e65ddc27bf63a88eb1fe","tid":1842123,"uid":19012,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T02:33:35.000Z","msg":"我有充份理由懷疑 777當年成日考第一 唔知用佐咩手段做free rider <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48fed97442d8558079c81072481286f68b79a9ba","tid":1842123,"uid":36739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a787c79e95aabf4799c3e65ddc27bf63a88eb1fe","tid":1842123,"uid":19012,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T02:33:35.000Z","msg":"我有充份理由懷疑 777當年成日考第一 唔知用佐咩手段做free rider <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T02:37:38.000Z","msg":"屌 可能係 <br />\n抄第二果個 第三果個 再集大成<br />\n有次唔比佢抄 所以第四<br />\n之後扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等人地借佢抄"},{"pid":"08c84966512ddcb41ff6d00343fe5f4a5f4dd8b0","tid":1842123,"uid":137999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f29d5d21fc354039bd35cf043c21db793531907b","tid":1842123,"uid":328778,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"77aa86ba5fc54a8446985a0b5037c1432ef2757d","tid":1842123,"uid":259010,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T14:06:57.000Z","msg":"6天蓋出「火神山醫院」不夠用！武漢決定旁邊再蓋一所「雷神山」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4669/d4669737.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4669%2Fd4669737.jpg&h=1816b700&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>▲為了再6天內蓋出「火神山醫院」，大陸調動上百台挖土機整地。（圖／新華網）</strong><br />\n記者蔡紹堅／綜合報導<br />\n武漢市防疫指揮部23日決定參照SARS期間7天建成的「小湯山醫院」，在6天內興建一所武漢肺炎的專門醫院，定名為「火神山醫院」。不過，似乎是考量到「火神山」的床位有限，武漢市防疫指揮部25日下午決定，要在2月5日前在「火神山」旁再建一所「雷神山醫院」。<br />\n「火神山醫院」的承建單位中建三局人員透露，火神山醫院的面積為2.5萬平方公尺，可容納1000張床，規劃在6天內建成，也就是說會在2月1日完工，2月3日投入使用。<br />\n<strong>▼挖土機通宵趕工，為了達成6天蓋出醫院的目標。（圖／新華網）</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4669/d4669734.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4669%2Fd4669734.jpg&h=9699b0e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為了達成6天完工的目標，中建三局23日晚上就展開動作，調集上百台挖土機、推土機等施工機械抵達工地，通宵進行場平、回填等施工。主體的施工則從25日開始，整個施工期間，項目部將按照兩班倒的方式日夜不停施工，高峰期將有1500名建設者和280台套施工機械設備同時奮戰。<br />\n不過，似乎是考量到「火神山醫院」的1000個床位不夠用，武漢市防疫指揮部25日下午3點半舉行調度會，決定在「火神山醫院」旁邊，在2月5日前再建成一所「雷神山醫院」，新增床位1300張。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4669/d4669716.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4669%2Fd4669716.jpg&h=fa4a9f18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>▲武漢肺炎疫情嚴峻，多名醫護也遭感染。（圖／武漢中心醫院）</strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T01:51:21.000Z","msg":"其實係焚化爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T02:37:51.000Z","msg":"好似挖緊坑，準備坑殺"},{"pid":"ecc228318e762524f10ffe594905c3a93b385cb0","tid":1842123,"uid":99172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T02:40:00.000Z","msg":"唔比人入 唔代表唔比人出喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2163f6106b56faca2ddbb9069bd52769eef357ee","tid":1842123,"uid":159870,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T02:41:32.000Z","msg":"輸澳門 輸深圳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係深圳人啊diu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df797c8d104458cb9ea64366372050667fab373","tid":1842123,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T02:43:40.000Z","msg":"樓主幫我置頂：<br />\n<br />\n林奠（後日）：宣佈沙頭角封關。"},{"pid":"a406cb7139cbda595f5174c93f95d340a6b54a4f","tid":1842123,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T02:45:22.000Z","msg":"我地靠深圳封城去封埋香港陸路口岸好似仲可行過<br />\n柒婆"},{"pid":"1728b6179c6a4267e1f49e73b788dd299496d2b0","tid":1842123,"uid":53003,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e6f144e8982a2d8607ba45f78a6f7cf7eea45f29","tid":1842123,"uid":236368,"like":439,"dislike":2,"score":437,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T14:04:42.000Z","msg":"屌，仲要係大陸個邊封<br />\n<br />\n香港真係垃圾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T02:47:04.000Z","msg":"一陣又比人spin做中央爺爺對香港幾好，為咗唔想香港人被感染而封關<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>"},{"pid":"4e58b8a7bcd1140d4207ddb2bbae8a5deefad4f4","tid":1842123,"uid":64126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T02:49:48.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">罷工唔止係醫護人員嘅責任<br />\n<br />\n係全香港700萬市民嘅責任<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全港三罷 刻不容緩</span><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oisbVO4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-s